            "title": "深水埗盲人按摩店女顧客拔罐搶火 背脊及手二級燒傷送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警員在按摩店調查。林思明攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/baf933e0d314a2471e645d43762754b8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032010061339000.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警員在按摩店調查。林思明攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>深水埗發生拔罐意外。今日（20日）早上8時56分，一名女子在長沙灣道47號地下一間盲人按摩店，進行按摩及拔火罐治療，其間懷疑職員噴灑精油突然搶火，火舌燒着女事主的背部，並波及睡床。職員見狀連忙將火撲熄，女事主背部及右手灼傷，報警求助。救護員到場將她送往明愛醫院治理，其間有女警陪同。現場消息稱，女事主經送院後證實二級燒傷，警方正調查事件原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4147795/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女傷者由救護車送院。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f0c54e84697f9a4ace3ac99eb11e14c0/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250320_095405271.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女傷者由救護車送院。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4147796/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女警陪同女傷者送院。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/196740ff3157487386d18314411758c0/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250320_095405271_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Ima